{"id": "webh_checkout", "modality": "web", "name": "Checkout", "task": {"description": "Build a checkout page for 'Checkout' at 1920px wide as a two-column layout: LEFT (60%) a form with three labeled sections (Contact, Shipping address with a 2x2 grid of fields, Payment with card-number/expiry/CVC fields) using aligned labels and inputs; RIGHT (40%) an order summary card that is sticky on scroll, listing 3 line items (name, qty, price), a promo-code input, and Subtotal $172.00 / Shipping $8.00 / Total $180.00, plus a full-width 'Pay $180.00' button. Responsive: at 375px the order summary moves below the form (not sticky), and the 2x2 address grid becomes single-column.", "requirements": ["A two-column layout: form (~60%) on the left and order summary (~40%) on the right, top-aligned", "The form has three clearly grouped sections (Contact, Shipping, Payment)", "Form fields have aligned labels and inputs; the shipping address uses a 2x2 field grid that lines up", "The order summary lists three line items each with name, qty, and price", "The order summary shows Subtotal $172.00, Shipping $8.00, Total $180.00 and a 'Pay $180.00' button", "The Total $180.00 and the Pay button amount match exactly", "The order summary is sticky on desktop scroll and does not overlap the form", "On desktop nothing overflows horizontally", "At 375px the order summary moves below the form and the 2x2 address grid becomes a single column", "Inputs share a consistent style and the Pay button is the highest-contrast action"], "difficulty": "hard"}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 6, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 3727, "rv_n_defects": 2, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 17892}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 6, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 3960, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 19366}, {"run": 3, "ss_n_defects": 6, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 3962, "rv_n_defects": 2, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 18591}], "ss_img": "images/web/webh_checkout_ss.jpg", "rv_img": "images/web/webh_checkout_rv.jpg", "ss_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Checkout</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            color: #1a1a1a;\n            background-color: #f8f9fa;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1920px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 48px 24px;\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: 60% 40%;\n            gap: 48px;\n            align-items: start;\n        }\n\n        .checkout-form {\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            padding: 48px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);\n        }\n\n        .order-summary {\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            padding: 32px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);\n            position: sticky;\n            top: 24px;\n        }\n\n        h1 {\n            font-size: 36px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            color: #1a1a1a;\n            margin-bottom: 48px;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .form-section {\n            margin-bottom: 48px;\n        }\n\n        .form-section:last-child {\n            margin-bottom: 0;\n        }\n\n        .section-title {\n            font-size: 24px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            color: #1a1a1a;\n            margin-bottom: 24px;\n            padding-bottom: 12px;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #e9ecef;\n        }\n\n        .form-group {\n            margin-bottom: 24px;\n        }\n\n        .form-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n            gap: 24px;\n        }\n\n        .payment-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr;\n            gap: 24px;\n        }\n\n        label {\n            display: block;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            font-weight: 500;\n            color: #495057;\n            margin-bottom: 8px;\n        }\n\n        input[type=\"text\"],\n        input[type=\"email\"],\n        input[type=\"tel\"] {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 16px;\n            border: 2px solid #e9ecef;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            transition: border-color 0.2s ease;\n            background: white;\n        }\n\n        input[type=\"text\"]:focus,\n        input[type=\"email\"]:focus,\n        input[type=\"tel\"]:focus {\n            outline: none;\n            border-color: #007bff;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        .order-summary h2 {\n            font-size: 24px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            color: #1a1a1a;\n            margin-bottom: 32px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .line-item {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: center;\n            padding: 16px 0;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;\n        }\n\n        .line-item:last-of-type {\n            border-bottom: none;\n            margin-bottom: 24px;\n        }\n\n        .item-details {\n            flex: 1;\n        }\n\n        .item-name {\n            font-size: 16px;\n            font-weight: 500;\n            color: #1a1a1a;\n            margin-bottom: 4px;\n        }\n\n        .item-qty {\n            font-size: 14px;\n            color: #6c757d;\n        }\n\n        .item-price {\n            font-size: 16px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            color: #1a1a1a;\n        }\n\n        .promo-section {\n            margin: 24px 0;\n            padding: 24px 0;\n            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;\n        }\n\n        .promo-input {\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 12px;\n        }\n\n        .promo-input input {\n            flex: 1;\n            padding: 12px 16px;\n            border: 2px solid #e9ecef;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            font-size: 14px;\n        }\n\n        .promo-btn {\n            padding: 12px 24px;\n            background: #6c757d;\n            color: white;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            font-weight: 500;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.2s ease;\n        }\n\n        .promo-btn:hover {\n            background: #5a6268;\n        }\n\n        .summary-line {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: center;\n            padding: 12px 0;\n            font-size: 16px;\n        }\n\n        .summary-line.total {\n            font-size: 20px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            color: #1a1a1a;\n            padding-top: 16px;\n            border-top: 2px solid #e9ecef;\n            margin-top: 16px;\n        }\n\n        .pay-button {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background: #007bff;\n            color: white;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            font-size: 18px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            margin-top: 32px;\n            transition: background-color 0.2s ease;\n        }\n\n        .pay-button:hover {\n            background: #0056b3;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 375px) {\n            .container {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n                gap: 32px;\n                padding: 24px 16px;\n            }\n\n            .checkout-form {\n                padding: 32px 24px;\n            }\n\n            .order-summary {\n                position: static;\n                order: 2;\n                padding: 24px;\n            }\n\n            h1 {\n                font-size: 28px;\n                margin-bottom: 32px;\n            }\n\n            .section-title {\n                font-size: 20px;\n                margin-bottom: 20px;\n            }\n\n            .form-section {\n                margin-bottom: 32px;\n            }\n\n            .form-grid {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n                gap: 20px;\n            }\n\n            .payment-grid {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n                gap: 20px;\n            }\n\n            .order-summary h2 {\n                font-size: 20px;\n                margin-bottom: 24px;\n            }\n\n            .promo-input {\n                flex-direction: column;\n            }\n\n            .promo-btn {\n                width: 100%;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"checkout-form\">\n            <h1>Checkout</h1>\n            \n            <div class=\"form-section\">\n                <h2 class=\"section-title\">Contact</h2>\n                <div class=\"form-group\">\n                    <label for=\"email\">Email address</label>\n                    <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" required>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"form-section\">\n                <h2 class=\"section-title\">Shipping address</h2>\n                <div class=\"form-grid\">\n           